n| nationalteam-update  = \n}}\n'''Iliyan Yordanov''' ([[Bulgarian language|Bulgarian]]: \u0418\u043b\u0438\u044f\u043d \u0419\u043e\u0440\u0434\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432; born 3 April 1989) is a [[Bulgaria]]n professional [[association football|footballer]] who currently plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[FC Maritsa Plovdiv|Maritsa Plovdiv]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=footballdatabase.eu|title=Ilian Yordanov Facts|url=http://www.footballdatabase.eu/football.joueurs.iliyan.yordanov.49561.en.html|accessdate=}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\nYordanov started his career at [[PFC Botev Plovdiv|Botev Plovdiv]] but left when the club went bankrupt in the early 2010 and subsequently joined [[Lyubimets 2007]]. During his career he also played abroad, first with Turkish side [[Denizlispor]] and then with Serbian side [[FK Borac \u010ca\u010dak|Borac \u010ca\u010dak]].<ref name=\"soccerway\">[https://int.soccerway.com/players/iliyan-yordanov/51672/ Iliyan Yordanov profile] at Soccerway</ref>\n\n==Honours==\n;Tsarsko Selo Sofia\n* [[Second Professional Football League (Bulgaria)|Bulgarian Second League]]: [[2018\u201319 Second Professional Football League (Bulgaria)|2018\u201319]]<ref name=\"soccerway\"/>\n\n;Lokomotiv Plovdiv\n* [[Bulgarian Cup]] runner-up: [[2011\u201312 Bulgarian Cup|2012]]<ref name=\"soccerway\"/>\n* [[Bulgarian Supercup]]: [[2012 Bulgarian Supercup|2012]]<ref name=\"soccerway\"/>\n\n;Levski Sofia\n* [[Bulgarian Cup]] runner-up: [[2012\u201313 Bulgarian Cup|2013]]<ref name=\"soccerway\"/>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://en.levskisofia.info/player/ilian-yordanov/ Profile at LevskiSofia.info]\n\n{{FC Maritsa Plovdiv squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Yordanov, Iliyan}}\n[[Category:1989 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Bulgarian footballers]]\n[[Category:Bulgarian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:PFC Botev Plovdiv players]]\n[[Category:Lyubimetz 2007 players]]\n[[Category:PFC Lokomotiv Plovdiv players]]\n[[Category:PFC Levski Sofia players]]\n[[Category:Denizlispor footballers]]\n[[Category:FK Borac \u010ca\u010dak players]]\n[[Category:FC Vereya players]]\n[[Category:FC Tsarsko Selo players]]\n[[Category:FC Maritsa Plovdiv players]]\n[[Category:First Professional Football League (Bulgaria) players]]\n[[Category:TFF First League players]]\n[[Category:Serbian SuperLiga players]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Bulgarian expatriate sportspeople in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Serbia]]\n[[Category:Bulgarian expatriate sportspeople in Serbia]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Plovdiv]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name                 = Iliyan Yordanov\n| image                = \n| caption              = \n| fullname             = Iliyan Yordanov Yordanov\n| birth_date           = {{birth date and age|1989|4|3|df=y}}\n| birth_place          = Zvanichevo, [[People's Republic of Bulgaria|Bulgaria]] \n| height               = {{height|m=1.76}}\n| position             = [[Winger (football)|Winger]]\n| currentclub          = [[FC Maritsa Plovdiv|Maritsa Plovdiv]] \n| clubnumber           = 19\n| youthyears1          = \n| youthclubs1          = [[PFC Botev Plovdiv|Botev Plovdiv]]\n| years1               = 2008\u20132010 | clubs1 = [[PFC Botev Plovdiv|Botev Plovdiv]]         | caps1 = 10 | goals1 = 1\n| years2               = 2010\u20132011 | clubs2 = [[FC Lyubimets 2007|Lyubimets 2007]]        | caps2 = 36 | goals2 = 2\n| years3               = 2012      | clubs3 = [[PFC Lokomotiv Plovdiv|Lokomotiv Plovdiv]] | caps3 = 14 | goals3 = 0\n| years4               = 2013      | clubs4 = [[PFC Levski Sofia|Levski Sofia]]           | caps4 = 32 | goals4 = 6\n| years5               = 2014\u20132015 | clubs5 = [[Denizlispor]]                             | caps5 = 36 | goals5 = 8\n| years6               = 2015      | clubs6 = [[PFC Lokomotiv Plovdiv|Lokomotiv Plovdiv]] | caps6 = 4  | goals6 = 0\n| years7  